name: SUMMONING CIRCLES | サモニングサークル

metadata.description:
Mysterious summoning circles have begun to appear in various locations, leaving people puzzled and intrigued. These circles are intricate designs etched into the ground, often surrounded by candles or other mystical artifacts. They seem to have an otherworldly energy about them, and many people believe that they are portals to another realm.
